│ cannot be used in PHI nodes because they represent abstract resources that  │
│ cannot be merged or selected between different control flow paths.\n\n2.    │
│ Analyzing `opt`'s Log: The log shows that GVN is performing PRE (Partial    │
│ Redundancy Elimination) and creating a PHI node to merge values from        │
│ different predecessors. The dumped IR after transformation shows a PHI node │
